SECTION RULES:
1. situation: 2-3 sentences, operator-level, no signal IDs, no metric IDs.
2. key_story: only when dominant_cluster_exists=true; otherwise set key_story to null.
3. group_narratives: one sentence per category listed in SIGNALS GROUPED BY CATEGORY above. Do not add categories absent from the payload.
4. signal_narratives: one concise sentence per rule_id from RULE IDS IN PAYLOAD. Do not add extra rule_ids.
5. watch_signals: maximum 2 entries; observation only (never recommendations). Use only ids from RULE IDS IN PAYLOAD or METRIC IDS IN PAYLOAD.

